  "text": "To do so, we looked to the CDC's general guidelines for program evaluation as a blueprint for the structure of this analysis. Program evaluation is subdivided into four key components: formative evaluation, process evaluation, impact evaluation, and outcome evaluation. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Formative evaluation occurred early in the inception of our program; the focus of this discussion will be the latter three components.",
